title: ICSI CSEET October 2026 Registration Opens!
content:
# ICSI CSEET October 2026 Registration Opens!

Ek important update hai! The Institute of Company Secretaries of India (ICSI) ne Company Secretary Executive Entrance Test (CSEET) October 2026 session ke liye registration shuru kar diya hai. Jo students Company Secretary banne ki journey shuru karna chahte hain, unke liye yeh pehla step hai.

Here are the key dates aur details:

*   **Registration Start Date:** February 16, 2026
*   **Last Date for Registration:** May 31, 2026
*   **Application Portal:** Registration exclusively through smash.icsi.edu
*   **Registration Fee:** INR 7500
*   **Enrollment Window (without late fee):** July 01, 2026, to August 07, 2026
*   **Enrollment Window (with late fee):** August 09, 2026, to August 20, 2026
*   **Exam Dates:** The examination is expected to be conducted in the first week of October 2026, but exact dates are yet to be announced by ICSI.

Candidates are advised to register well before the deadline to avoid any last-minute rush. Detailed eligibility criteria and application instructions are available on the official portal.

## Read the Official Document
*   [Download the Official Notification/Circular here](https://smash.icsi.edu/)

*Published on: 16 February 2026*
